text: Trans is a village in the municipality of Tomils of the district Hinterrhein in the canton of Graubünden in Switzerland. In 2009 Trans joined Feldis/Veulden, Scheid and Tumegl/Tomils to become the municipality of Tomils. == Other websites == * Official Website * Category:Former municipalities of Graubünden Category:Villages in Graubünden
